<section>
  <title><indexterm significance="normal">
      <primary>site types</primary>
      <secondary>creating new</secondary>
    </indexterm>Site Type</title>
  <para>To create a new Site Type, select the NEW button. The following screen
  will appear:</para>
  <para><screenshot>
      <mediaobject>
        <imageobject>
          <imagedata fileref="images/siteType.png" />
        </imageobject>
        <caption>Create New Site Type</caption>
      </mediaobject>
    </screenshot></para>
  <para>When creating a new Site Type, you are presented with the following
  options:</para>
  <variablelist>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>Code</term>
      <listitem>
        <para>Enter a unique code to identify the Site Type.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>Description</term>
      <listitem>
        <para>Enter a description to further identify the Site Type.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
  </variablelist>
</section>
